dct_title_s: Insurance maps of the New Jersey coast : volume two
dct_description_sm: Index for maps of Deal, Allenhurst, Loch Arbour, West Allenhurst and Interlaken; Asbury Park and West Asbury Park; Ocean Grove, W. Ocean Grove, Bradley Beach, Bradley Park and Neptune City; Avon; and Belmar. Index sheet; map sheets foldered separately under name of town.
